notes:
[Outland Colossus] is the pick as it is one of the best cards in the set. I mean it's a 6/6 for 5 that your opponent can't double block, which is great... and that's before talking about the "Renown 6".

The runner up is [Supression Bonds] over [Leaf Gilder], because removal is important even if it's unexciting.
